@startuml Document Replace

title POST /documents/{id}/replace — 문서 교체

actor Client
participant "FastAPI\n(documents.py)" as API
participant "FileStorage\n(local.py)" as FS
participant "indexing.py" as IDX
participant "QdrantStore" as QD
database "SQLite/PG\n(DB)" as DB

Client -> API : POST /documents/{id}/replace\n(file)
activate API

API -> DB : GET Document by id
DB --> API : document

API -> IDX : clear_document_index(document)
activate IDX
IDX -> QD : delete_document(document_id)\n[payload filter]
QD --> IDX : ok
deactivate IDX

API -> FS : delete_document_dir(document_id)
note right of FS #pink
  ⚠ 여기서 실패하면 구 벡터는 삭제됐으나
  구 파일은 남는 불일치 발생 가능
end note

API -> FS : save_document_file(document_id, new_file)
FS --> API : StoredFile

API -> DB : flush (source_filename, mime_type,\nfile_path, size_bytes, sha256,\nstatus=pending, error=None)

API -> IDX : index_document(db, document)
activate IDX
note right of IDX
  ingest → embed → Qdrant upsert
  (동기 실행)
end note
IDX --> API : (status=ready or failed)
deactivate IDX

API -> DB : COMMIT

API --> Client : 200 DocumentOut

deactivate API

@enduml
